WEBVTT

00:00:00.070 --> 00:00:03.000
Words appear: Morevna School.
Animation workshops of "Adamant" Art School.

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:08.100
Based on a true story.

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:14.000
In animation, a boy sits in the stern of a small boat.
A purple head sits in the bow.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:25.000
With the head are arms, legs, and a body.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:28.000
The boat approaches a waterfall
with a sign: "Deadline"

00:00:31.422 --> 00:00:33.000
The boat shoots into the air.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:35.920
As it falls, the boy attaches body, arms, and legs.

00:00:35.932 --> 00:00:36.871
The head is below the body.

00:00:36.873 --> 00:00:37.754
The legs face the wrong way.

00:00:37.756 --> 00:00:39.900
An arm is in the head.

00:00:48.500 --> 00:00:50.000
Together they fall.

00:00:50.232 --> 00:00:52.740
Cut to black.


